title: LBOCN
description:
The light between oceans by M.L.Steadman

Once upon a time there was a lighthouse....

Tom Sherbourne psycholigically scarred by the first wold war returns to Australia , and gets a job as the lightkeeper on an isolated island.
 He seems to get a new lease on life by marrying the young Isabel. Three miscarriages later, Isabel hears a baby's cry on the wind, a boat has washed up with a baby and a dead man. 

Against Tom's judgement the baby is claimed as their own, a decision that will change their lives irrevocably.

A soulful and heartbreaking narrative, so little light so much darkness.

bit rate 48 kbps
